    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/09ebce540f4784588fe9f14b44d6b137.poster.avif?t=1701830436\" width=480 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/09ebce540f4784588fe9f14b44d6b137.webm?t=1701830436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/09ebce540f4784588fe9f14b44d6b137.mp4?t=1701830436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>致命梦魇是参与恐怖和精彩的，或者生存游戏在哪里您游戏一个男儿住在大庄园。你可以用工具为了探索世界，在种类具有挑战性的找到谜团和探索，害怕和超自然地点。你想什么东四揭开真相吗？只要你知道的，因为继续和享受游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/d61501f5fd195aba0c231d7a6f80c277.poster.avif?t=1701830436\" width=480 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/d61501f5fd195aba0c231d7a6f80c277.webm?t=1701830436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/d61501f5fd195aba0c231d7a6f80c277.mp4?t=1701830436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>精彩故事<br>在可怕的噩梦中主角是奶奶，她去世了。在她的意志写了在他们的家庭绑诅咒。以后他们去世了，诅咒进入她的身体。我们取决于，男孩可以打破家庭诅咒的。你只要6个小时留下来活着和生存，以后诅咒会进入女仆和男孩身体。我们需要探索在游戏地位，因该找到诅咒之书的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/550fa65f53e0f0325686a410158bee20.poster.avif?t=1701830436\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/550fa65f53e0f0325686a410158bee20.webm?t=1701830436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/550fa65f53e0f0325686a410158bee20.mp4?t=1701830436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>强，游戏点有益<br>我们需要探索在庄园，找到诅咒之书。我们需要制造咒语和诅咒，就可以保护我们免受魔鬼的力量，一次我们可以做这样的。也是我们需要结束主要任务叫《诅咒之门》。意思是我们找到了这些材料可以打开诅咒门口。大冒险对您是在做找到和尝试打败诅咒女王是主要挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/7633dc182035660538c516067c7dfac3.poster.avif?t=1701830436\" width=480 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/7633dc182035660538c516067c7dfac3.webm?t=1701830436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/7633dc182035660538c516067c7dfac3.mp4?t=1701830436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>实验各种各样的咒语<br>在我们真生化也有咒语致命梦魇，它们在游戏未用灵感的。但是最多是虚构的咒语适合故事中和提供独特的包含激动人心和有趣是你们期望的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/c9c5fe8253fd2e74e85b3638cf67775d.poster.avif?t=1701830436\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/c9c5fe8253fd2e74e85b3638cf67775d.webm?t=1701830436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/c9c5fe8253fd2e74e85b3638cf67775d.mp4?t=1701830436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>找到和用工具和材料<br>这个比较帮助您，还是你需要它们为了动自己在故事。感兴趣和有益的，有趣，也很容易进入。但是，你也可以找到一些毒药，还可以用为了超自然的力量。<br>庄园本很恐怖和一种公平挑战的。你有什么办法这次或者永逸对探索和解决吗？今天肯定使用致命梦魇！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/6b9ed9dd04ae1012ff2dd228b34c73f3.poster.avif?t=1701830436\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/6b9ed9dd04ae1012ff2dd228b34c73f3.webm?t=1701830436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828010/extras/6b9ed9dd04ae1012ff2dd228b34c73f3.mp4?t=1701830436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>特点：<br>探索庄园和移除诅咒<br>制造诅咒和咒语跟酷的效果<br>带材料和工具<br>使用毒药获得超自然力量",
